The ‘Arc of The Possible’, a book written by Waziri Adio, can be purchased in several physical and online book stores across Nigeria. Published by Cable Books, the memoir was released on December 01 and publicly presented on December 11. In the memoir, Waziri Adio, former executive secretary of the Nigeria Extractive Industries Transparency Initiative (NEITI), chronicles his experience in office. ‘Arc of the The Possible’ has been applauded by critics and Japheth Omojuwa, chief strategist at Alpha Reach, recently said it should be recommended for those in public office. You can purchase a copy of the book at Patabah Bookstore, Roving Heights Bookstore, Readers are Leaders Bookstore or any of the bookstores below:  Adeniran Ogunsanya St, Surulere.  Off Sultan Abubakar Way, Wuse Zone 2 